1. Upload Website Files
The developer uploads HTML, CSS, JS, and images into an S3 bucket.

2. Enable Static Website Hosting
The S3 bucket is configured to host a static website with an index document and error document.

3. Apply Bucket Policy
A public-read policy is attached to allow website users to access the files.
